{
  "stem": "22463.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a new law that there have to be at least five.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have to have one-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --Ukrainian soldier who was escorting us and stay over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was in a very bad position because after the [NON-ENGLISH], I haven't got-- I haven't got a place to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very danger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I fortunately have a friend of mine who was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --a kind of [? porter ?] in-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --employment office.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He told me it is very bad because there are only three places calling for worker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The one was the [NON-ENGLISH] and the other one was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were all-- all about 100 kilometers from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Doesn't-- doesn't-- I doesn't want to-- to part with my wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he told me there are other places I might [? find ?] [? work ?].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But people are not working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not because they don't want to work, but because they are running away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They don't last a while anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I tell him, listen, when-- I know the-- the factory from [INAUDIBLE], when I can find the people I had been dealing with, I can manage, maybe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Send me over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I get-- they get a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And by this, then, I-- I come over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When I come over to the-- to the gate-- to the gate with-- the people who had been going-- going with me, on the-- on the gate, I find [INAUDIBLE], the engineer of press room.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he-- I know him from the war, very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was a alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But had a way very, very, very gentle and honest man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
